OL,3,CVictim's fight for reform after abuser
OL,4,Cruled unfit for trial
OL,6,FSimon Byrne was sexually abused by a
OL,7,Fboxing coach as a child, he tells Emma
OL,8,FSweeney about his fight to get justice.
OL,10,FA man whose childhood abuse case
OL,11,Fcollapsed when his attacker was
OL,12,Fdeclared unfit to stand trial says
OL,13,Fvictims are being failed by the
OL,14,Fjustice system.
OL,16,FSimon Byrne was just 11 when he joined
OL,17,FSharston Amateur Boxing Club in
OL,18,FWythenshawe, Manchester in the early
OL,19,F1980s.
