OL,3,CVictim's fight for reform after abuser
OL,4,Cruled unfit for trial
OL,6,FWhat began as a "massive adventure",
OL,7,Fhe says, quickly turned into a five-
OL,8,Fyear campaign of sexual abuse by the
OL,9,Fclub's owner, Patrick Lowe.
OL,11,F"When I started, it was a massive
OL,12,Fadventure to me", Mr Bryne recalled.
OL,14,F"Some older friends who my dad had
OL,15,Fstarted boxing with years earlier went
OL,16,Fto the club, and it was exciting to be
OL,17,Fout with them."
OL,19,F"But one night out of the blue, I was
OL,20,Fcalled in to be weighed - and that's
OL,21,Fwhen it first started.
