OL,6,F"I was that young and innocent, I
OL,7,Fdidn't really realise what was going
OL,8,Fon. I knew it was wrong, but didn't
OL,9,Freally know why."
OL,11,FMr Byrne said Lowe used threats to
OL,12,Fkeep him silent.
OL,14,F"He'd say how you might be sent away.
OL,15,FI can make your family get into
OL,16,Ftrouble," Mr Byrne said.
OL,18,F"I can make you disappear. It's real
OL,19,Fdark, nasty, horrible stuff. As a
OL,20,Fchild, you know, you do believe."
