OL,6,FThe trauma stayed with Mr Byrne for
OL,7,Fdecades, leading to a mental health
OL,8,Fbreakdown.
OL,10,FIt was only then, after 30 years of
OL,11,Fkeeping his abuse a secret, that he
OL,12,Ffinally felt able to speak out and
OL,13,Freport it to the police.
OL,15,FBut the case moved painfully slowly.
OL,16,FIt took two years for Lowe to be
OL,17,Fcharged, and another two years before
OL,18,Fit was due in court.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
