OL,6,FAs Mr Byrne travelled from his home in
OL,7,FIreland last November to attend the
OL,8,Ftrial, he got the "devastating" phone
OL,9,Fcall to say Lowe had developed
OL,10,Fdementia and was unfit to stand trial.
OL,12,FBut the former amateur boxer refused
OL,13,Fto give up. He pushed for what's known
OL,14,Fas a "trial of fact" hearing - a legal
OL,15,Fprocess which allows a jury to
OL,16,Fdetermine whether offences were
OL,17,Fcommitted when a defendant is deemed
OL,18,Funfit to face criminal proceedings.
OL,26,@vD@FOUvD@TO]
