OL,3,CVictim's fight for reform after abuser
OL,4,Cruled unfit for trial
OL,6,FThe jury found Patrick Lowe, who is
OL,7,Fnow 86, had committed the offences. It
OL,8,Fwas also mentioned at the hearing that
OL,9,FLowe has a previous conviction for a
OL,10,Fsimilar offence.
OL,12,FHe was placed on the sex offender's
OL,13,Fregister for five years, but the trial
OL,14,Fjudge was "limited" with what else he
OL,15,Fcould do.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
