OL,3,CVictim's fight for reform after abuser
OL,4,Cruled unfit for trial
OL,6,FBarrister Chloe Fordham, who
OL,7,Fprosecuted the case, said: "Due to Mr
OL,8,FLowe having been found unfit to plead
OL,9,Fand being diagnosed with a condition
OL,10,Fthat would not respond to treatment,
OL,11,Fthe judge had very limited options.
OL,13,F"These were an absolute discharge or a
OL,14,Fsupervision order but, realistically,
OL,15,Fthe latter was not an option as there
OL,16,Fwas no constructive work that the
OL,17,FProbation Service could have done with
OL,18,FMr Lowe in the community."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
