OL,6,FAt the end of the case, His Honour
OL,7,FJudge Usher, said: "I don't find this
OL,8,Foutcome satisfactory as it runs the
OL,9,Frisk of trivialising the seriousness
OL,10,Fof what he did.
OL,12,F"The law around this type of trial is
OL,13,Fbeing reviewed and may change in the
OL,14,Ffuture."
OL,26,@oD@TOUtD@AOUvD@HO]
