OL,6,FAlmost a year on from when the trial
OL,7,Fshould have taken place, Simon and his
OL,8,Fwife Maria are campaigning for change
OL,9,F- they want to see courts sitting on
OL,10,Fweekends to help clear the backlog,
OL,11,Fthey want more victims to be aware of
OL,12,Ffact-finding hearings and they also
OL,13,Fwant new laws on how elderly or unwell
OL,14,Fabusers are dealt with.
OL,16,F"We want there to be secure care homes
OL,17,Ffor them," Maria said. "If they're not
OL,18,Fsuitable for prison, then have them
OL,19,Fsomewhere safe, with carers who are
OL,20,Fproperly trained."
OL,26,@xD@AOUyD@JO]yD@XOU|D@RO]
