OL,6,FThe couple have written to the Prime
OL,7,FMinister and Justice Secretary urging
OL,8,Fchange.
OL,10,F"They can't change what happened to
OL,11,Fme," Mr Byrne said. "But I don't want
OL,12,Fanyone else to go through what we went
OL,13,Fthrough ` and for it to end with
OL,14,Fnothing."
OL,16,FA Greater Manchester Police
OL,17,Fspokesperson said: "We understand that
OL,18,Fthe length of investigations can add
OL,19,Fto the trauma suffered by survivors of
OL,20,Fsexual abuse, and we share victims'
OL,21,Fdesire to see offenders behind bars.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@DO]sD@UOUvD@IO]yD@TOU
