OL,6,F"We are open with survivors from the
OL,7,Fstart about the complexity and lengths
OL,8,Fof investigations, and we work with
OL,9,Fsupporting agencies to try and ensure
OL,10,Fvictims are kept updated throughout.
OL,12,F"Every line of enquiry in this complex
OL,13,Finvestigation was followed which
OL,14,Fresulted in a strong file being
OL,15,Fsubmitted to the CPS and charges being
OL,16,Fsecured.
OL,18,FBringing abusers to justice is why our
OL,19,Finvestigation teams work so tirelessly
OL,20,Fday-in day out.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
