OL,6,F"Time will be no barrier to GMP's
OL,7,Fcommitment to seeking justice for
OL,8,Fsurvivors."
OL,10,FA Ministry of Justice spokesperson
OL,11,Fsaid: "The Government inherited a
OL,12,Fjustice system in crisis, and a record
OL,13,Fcourt backlog means victims are
OL,14,Fwaiting too long for justice.
OL,16,FWe are looking at once in-a-generation
OL,17,Freforms and funding record levels of
OL,18,FCrown Court sitting days to fix this
OL,19,Fbroken system and get victims the
OL,20,Fjustice they deserve."
